448
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,880
This area has treacherous terrain.

449
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:04,640
Won't it be too dangerous?

450
00:42:04,640 --> 00:42:05,320
No problem.

451
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:08,000
Our Seventh Detachment guerrilla fighters

452
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,760
They're all locals from Zhongshan

